data.description: Presenting this 1638 sq ft single family home with a 2 car attached garage. Located in a great neighborhood that is close to shopping, restaurants, and recreational activities.  The home does require some TLC and a few updates but it has endless potential. There is a deck overlooking a spacious back yard. Don't pass up the opportunity to own a home in this fantastic location.
